                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character\u2019s hands lack the strength to hold a bow taut or hurl a dagger with force, resulting in limp shots that barely reach the target. They\u2019ve dropped more throwing knives than they\u2019ve thrown, much to the amusement of onlookers. Even gripping a mug takes effort some days. Their aim suffers from their feeble grasp.",
